OL,3,CHansen hoped to make 'full recovery'
OL,4,Cformer Liverpool teammate says
OL,6,FAlan Hansen's former teammate says he
OL,7,Fhopes the Liverpool legend is on the
OL,8,Froad to 'a full recovery' after
OL,9,Freceiving a phone call where he
OL,10,F'sounded fabulous' from his hospital
OL,11,Fbed.
OL,13,FThe former Liverpool and Scotland
OL,14,Fdefender remains in hospital after
OL,15,Fbeing taken seriously ill on 9 June.
OL,17,FGiving an update on his condition,
OL,18,FGraeme Souness says he had a
OL,19,Fconversation with Hansen and is
OL,20,Fhopeful his old colleague is now on
OL,21,Fthe road to recovery.
