OL,3,CHansen hoped to make 'full recovery'
OL,4,Cformer Liverpool teammate says
OL,6,F"I spoke to him yesterday and he
OL,7,Fsounded fabulous so I hope that's him
OL,8,Fon the way to a full recovery," former
OL,9,FLiverpool manager Souness said.
OL,11,FSpeaking on the talkSPORT breakfast
OL,12,Fshow to host Jim White he added: "He's
OL,13,Fdefinitely back because he did nothing
OL,14,Fbut take the Mickey out of me!
OL,16,F"I've been speaking to his son and
OL,17,FJanet his wife and I've been phoning
OL,18,Fhis phone, his phone number.
