OL,3,CHansen hoped to make 'full recovery'
OL,4,Cformer Liverpool teammate says
OL,6,F"I got on the train on Sunday and I
OL,7,Fwas looking for my seat and my phone
OL,8,Frang and I could see it was Big Al. I
OL,9,Fwas thinking 'Oh no, don't answer
OL,10,Fthat'.
OL,12,F"So I sat down and got the courage to
OL,13,Fphone back and HE answered the phoned.
OL,15,F"He's been in a difficult place but
OL,16,Fthe way he sounded yesterday, he's
OL,17,Fback, and I hope I'm right."
