OL,6,FA statement released by the club on
OL,7,FSunday 9 June read: "The thoughts and
OL,8,Fsupport of everyone at Liverpool FC
OL,9,Fare with our legendary former captain
OL,10,FAlan Hansen, who is currently
OL,11,Fseriously ill in hospital.
OL,13,F"The club is currently in contact with
OL,14,FAlan's family to provide our support
OL,15,Fat this difficult time, and our
OL,16,Fthoughts, wishes and hopes are with
OL,17,FAlan and all of the Hansen family.
